#Tests:Contains all test cases that validate application functionality by calling methods from page classes.
#Utilities:Stores common reusable functions like explicit waits, implicit waits, screenshot capture, custom logging, test data handling, and helper methods.
#conftest.py:Used for defining fixtures like browser setup and teardown, reusable test configurations, and shared test resources across multiple test files.
#pytest.ini:Used for pytest configuration such as markers, command-line options, test discovery rules, and default settings.
#requirements.txt:Contains all required Python packages and dependencies needed to run the framework.